 Shaggy 2 Dope，”活动中的一位粉丝说道。 “我会把它们放在白宫里。”</p><p>您可以在上面观看完整视频。</p><p>其他认可哈里斯的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a> 、布鲁斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-endorses-kamala-harris-for-us-president-ive-only-got-one-vote-and-its-one-of-the-most-precious-possessions-that-i-have-3799537">·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查理·XCX (Charli XCX)</a> 、查佩尔·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-freedom-soundtracks-kamala-harris-first-presidential-election-campaign-video-3777987">碧昂丝 (Beyoncé)</a> 、梅根·西·斯塔林 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">Megan Thee Stallion</a> )、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、邦·伊弗 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">Bon Iver)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">夸沃 (Quavo)</a> 、比莉·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">芬尼斯 (Finneas)</a> 。</p><p>在 11 月 5 日美国总统大选之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-to-headline-kamala-harris-rallies-in-atlanta-and-philadelphia-3805409">，斯普林斯汀将分别在明天（10 月 24 日）和星期一（28 日）在亚特兰大和费城举行的哈里斯集会上担任主角</a>。</p><p>其他新闻方面，昨晚（10 月 22 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">，巴拉克·奥巴马 (Barack Obama) 在说唱歌手家乡底特律举行的哈里斯集会上，由阿姆 (Eminem) 